                     <interp inst="t18300415-224-off1241" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <placeName id="t18300415-224-crimeloc1242">6th of April</placeName>
                     <interp inst="t18300415-224-crimeloc1242" type="placeName" value="6th of April"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300415-224-crimeloc1242" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-224-off1241 t18300415-224-crimeloc1242"></join>, 1 watch, value 20s.; 1 seal, value 5s.; 1 watch-chain, value 20s., and 2 watch-keys, value 2s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18300415-224-victim1968" type="victimName">
